## ğŸ”§ Features

- ğŸ§  Send and receive messages using an API-based LLM
- âœï¸ Rewrite user input intelligently
- ğŸ‹ï¸â€â™‚ï¸ Train a local intent classification model
- ğŸ” Detect user intent with confidence scoring

